Package Admin

package Admin
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AdminApp
    [Admin Module] Admin Starter App containing list of Admin Functions.
    CineplexApp
    [Admin Module] Cineplex App under Configure System Settings.
    HolidayApp
    [Admin Module] Holiday App under Configure System Settings.
    LoginApp
    [Admin Module] Login App for users to enter their credentials to use the admin system.
    MovieListingApp
    [Admin Module] Movie Listing App containing CRUD functions for Movies.
    SettingApp
    [Admin Module] Configure Settings App.
    ShowtimeApp
    [Admin Module] Showtime App containing CRUD functions for Movie ShowTimes.
    TicketPricingApp
    [Admin Module] Ticket Pricing App to control the modifiers affecting ticket prices (i.e., movie type, cinema class, etc.).
    TopFiveApp
    [Admin Module] Top-Five App to configure settings to allow movie-goers to list top 5 movie listings based on filter (i.e., ticket sales, review ratings).
